item.title: Open Coroporates Test
item.description: Introduction As per application requirements I will be analysing the data set in accordance with prescribed guidelines. There are three major points to adhere to: div.grey { background-color:#3d4849; border-radius: 5px; padding: 20px;} Identify 3-5 interesting facts from the data set Identify at least 3 of the errors within the data set Explain rationale and methodology via code chunks and prose. Tabset is incompatible with Hugo, so this is one LONG scroll.
